OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be mainly dry with the odd shower
OL,7,Fin the north. Then rather cloudy
OL,8,Fovernight with a little light and
OL,9,Fpatchy rain in the north and east.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FA dry day on Thursday with
OL,12,Fsome bright or sunny spells developing
OL,13,Fby afternoon. Warm.
OL,14,
OL,15,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FDry and
OL,16,Fbright on Friday. Cloudy with rain on
OL,17,FSaturday, drier with a few showers
OL,18,Flater. Mainly dry on Sunday.
